			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">SERC have recently introduced a scheme whereby IRCs may apply for an earmarked allocation of VFs.  The rate of VF applications from CPSE has recently increased as a result of two factors:  our ability to accommodate more visitors since we took over our new space and the ever growing recognition of the IRC in the community.  In addition, the quality of the cases put forward means that they are usually approved.  Therefore, it would be more convenientfrom an administrative point of view to make a block provision of VFs to CPSE. Also, having a block allocation will enable us to respond more quickly to opportunities to attract excellent people.</span>
                        </td>
